OL,3,CHuge Merthyr sinkhole increases in
OL,4,Csize as water levels in culvert rise
OL,6,FA huge sinkhole has appeared on a
OL,7,Fsouth Wales housing estate leading to
OL,8,F30 homes being evacuated.
OL,10,FPeople are being urged to stay away
OL,11,Fafter the 50ft hole appeared at Nant
OL,12,FMorlais, Pant, Merthyr, today, 1
OL,13,FDecember.
OL,15,FCouncil officers and police are on the
OL,16,Fsite working with other agencies.
