OL,3,CHuge Merthyr sinkhole increases in
OL,4,Csize as water levels in culvert rise
OL,6,FA statement from Merthyr Council said:
OL,7,F"No further help or support is needed
OL,8,Fat this time but thank you to everyone
OL,9,Fwho has offered it. Safety is our main
OL,10,Fpriority."
OL,12,FThey also issued a warning, saying:
OL,13,F"To allow engineers to keep working
OL,14,Fsafely, please stay away from the
OL,15,Farea."
OL,17,FThere was heavy rain in parts of Wales
OL,18,Fovernight, just days after Storm Bert
OL,19,Fcaused devastation across parts of the
OL,20,Fcountry.
