OL,3,CHuge Merthyr sinkhole increases in
OL,4,Csize as water levels in culvert rise
OL,6,FLocal councillor David Hughes said
OL,7,Fresidents of Nant Morlais - about 30
OL,8,Fhomes - have been evacuated. The cul-
OL,9,Fde-sac has been closed and people are
OL,10,Fbeing advised to avoid the area.
OL,12,FIt is unclear how long the street will
OL,13,Fbe evacuated for.
OL,15,FA police statement said: "South Wales
OL,16,FPolice are dealing with a incident on
OL,17,FNant Morlais, Pant, Merthyr. The road
OL,18,Fis currently closed in both
OL,19,Fdirections. Please avoid the area."
